{"tid":1913685,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁凌杰 (1984年3月7日－2019年6月15日）","createTime":"2020-03-07T04:10:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T06:38:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"773dd38e1a9d9266717673735dd65df612976844","tid":1913685,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:10:26.000Z","msg":"&quot;2019年6月15日下午4時許，梁凌杰穿着背上寫有「林鄭殺港 黑警冷血」的黃色雨衣，站在金鐘太古廣場4樓平台，在廣場外牆工作枱的棚架上掛上「反送中 No Extradition To China」、「全面撤回送中，我們不是暴動，釋放學生傷者，林鄭下台，Help Hong Kong」的抗議標語[7]。他抗議林鄭月娥及警方聲稱6月12日的佔領行動為暴動，並要求撤回條例草案（而非暫緩）、釋放在警民衝突中的被捕人士及特首林鄭月娥引咎辭職。消防員接報後在現場打開救生氣墊[8]。<br />\n<br />\n危站期間，在場市民不停大叫：「聽日我哋一齊遊行，唔好死呀，撐住呀。」（明日我等一齊遊行，不要死啊，撐下去）。立法會議員鄺俊宇其後到場支援，曾三度向警察要求與梁凌杰直接對話，以勸喻對方返回安全地方，惟遭警方拒絕，僅表示有警察談判組在現場。然而，梁亦一直不願意與警方的談判專家交談[2]。鄺俊宇在金鐘道對面用揚聲器叫喊，然而聲音未能清楚傳到現場[9]。現場亦有數名市民唱起《Sing hallelujah to the Lord》詩歌[10]。時至夜晚8時許，梁凌杰脫下黃衣坐在平台休息，持盾警員及消防員於樓上戒備[4]。約9時，梁凌杰爬出棚架，消防員嘗試將他拉回不果，梁最終墮下，跌於氣墊旁之行人路[4]。在場市民在消防員胸外心臟按壓搶救不時高叫「撐住呀！」，目睹過程的鄺俊宇激動痛哭[11][12]。他被送往律敦治醫院搶救後證實不治[13]。梁凌杰為反對修例運動中首名死者[14]。<br />\n<br />\n事後身上發現兩封遺書，闡述尋死原因是和訴求反對修例有關，以及交代身後事[2]。&quot;"},{"pid":"1925464a582b0e7a2ba3333be4b36511efc390e0","tid":1913685,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJoTMRh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJoTMRh.jpg&h=607195cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"487925607170da548d642b34742346db9499800f","tid":1913685,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1925464a582b0e7a2ba3333be4b36511efc390e0","tid":1913685,"uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJoTMRh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJoTMRh.jpg&h=607195cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78230ad8a2251f9a4b3b433524df0b9e063de94c","tid":1913685,"uid":114360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:21:44.000Z","msg":"不知不覺間，今日係梁烈士嘅生忌<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913659</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請幫手推post"},{"pid":"e3b16456281a8e4f6800df47adfd78fb01622ce4","tid":1913685,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T04:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d44435772d81c2e7cfd19b464de8ff48626d1cd6","tid":1913685,"uid":116074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-07T06:38:42.000Z","msg":"佢個生忌邊度流出黎？"}]}